{"tid":1422960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"麻煩各位幫手 -- 民間記者會 文宣 資料收集","createTime":"2019-08-06T12:29:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T12:49:33.000Z","uid":138409,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0e80c75d9d53fc2885ff817133af07a014600f76","tid":1422960,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:29:14.000Z","msg":"轉載自哨兵channel<br />\n----------------------<br />\n大家好<br />\n<br />\n有手足成立咗民間記者會多媒體工作小組 <br />\n<br />\n佢哋需要大量素材製作民間記者會嘅多媒體影片／剪報<br />\n請大家幫手up 片<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/JaHJs6XE4y8UCfV79\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FJaHJs6XE4y8UCfV79&d=Lhg6HStjEOrAYLon%2F%2F44J34HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=c1a0b915\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/JaHJs6XE4y8UCfV79</a><br />\n<br />\n片可以係一手（直播捕捉唔到嘅鏡頭）或者二手（手足從直播片段cut出黎嘅片)**<br />\n<br />\n上傳嘅圖片或者影片我哋會留底 但係絕對唔會收集各位嘅個人資料如電郵等（<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">建議使用分身email</span></span>）<br />\n素材會根據唔同嘅記者會主題而採用 <br />\n<br />\n**請於檔案名稱註明出處<br />\n<br />\n多謝咁多位手足！<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力！"},{"pid":"d2bfeb999bcdcdc8969fc4895cec2437316d9d95","tid":1422960,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:30:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"22a78d1dcfd4a0a149407c30dc792a72f35e6c75","tid":1422960,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:32:02.000Z","msg":"（突發）（多圖） 炮台山勁多狗同狗車<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1422223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1422223</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"33cdaa7f4163393f551399ecc64c04c7a534c108","tid":1422960,"uid":280349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:33:09.000Z","msg":"「緊急號外」紅底理論upgrade 左，要拆解一下<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1422647\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1422647</a>"},{"pid":"888b49371b0a6c9cf22c046babb471d038062afe","tid":1422960,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s